Chelsea’s Target Villas-Boas Quits as Porto’s Coach, Lusa News Agency Says

-- B y   A l e x   D u f f
-- 
2011-06-21T10:45:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-21/chelsea-s-target-villas-boas-quits-as-porto-s-coach-lusa-news-agency-says.html
Andre Villas-Boas quit as coach of
Portuguese soccer champion Porto, clearing the way for him to
join Chelsea, the Lusa news agency reported, citing team sources
it didn’t identify.  Villas-Boas, in a fax sent to Porto, agreed to pay the
recision fee in his contract, Lusa said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alex Duff at 
 aduff4@bloomberg.net  